&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Build the Path Forward&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Path Robotics, we’re building the future of embodied intelligence. Our AI-driven systems enable robots to adapt, learn, and perform in the real world closing the skilled labor gap and transforming industries. We go beyond traditional methods, combining perception, reasoning, and control to deliver field-ready AI that is risk-aware, reliable, and continuously improving through real-world use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Big, hard problems are our everyday work, and our team of intelligent, humble, and driven people make the impossible possible together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Our Deployment Engineers work to seamlessly integrate our robots, sensors, and software into a cutting-edge autonomous welding system. They&#39;re the link between engineering and operations manufacturing groups as we prepare our robotic weld cells for deployment. You will report to our Senior Manager of Deployment Engineering and will join a team of dedicated, supportive, and enthusiastic people to help create the future of manufacturing.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Configure and calibrate cell components to confirm our robotic welding cells are fully operational at Path’s manufacturing facility and the customer site&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Identify software issues and implement fixes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Document system errors and submit Jira tickets for issues that require engineering team support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Work with the engineering team to continually improve speed and stability of the software releases&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Update documentation of cell operation and bring-up task processes as needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Train Operating Technicians on new operation processes as needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
