&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, or equivalent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in C++, Python, Bash, ROS, and Git version control&lt;/li&gt;
